      "raw_text": "Northern Pacific will inaugurate their\nSunday excursions to Occur d'Alene\nCity and st. Maries. Sunday train\nwill leave at n. m. returning to\nSpokane at p. m. The steamer\nGeorge Cakes. the largest and most\nsteamer on the lake. will\nmake the trip Occur dAlene to Har-\nrison. Chatcalet and St. Maries and\nreturn. connecting with train both\nways; fare for the entire round trip.\nsl.so. Finest trip for days ride to\nbe found.\n\n\nj. w. HII.f. General Agent."
    }
